{{> container-start}}
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      This is a gentle reminder that the
      payment for your billing period
      {{stringify-month month}}
      {{year}}
      is incomplete since you haven't added
      any payment method on your workspace
      <strong
        class="txt-light"
        style="color:#ffffff"
      >{{workspaceName}}</strong>.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      Total usage charges for
      {{stringify-month month}}
      {{year}}
      are:
      <a
        href="https://app.patr.cloud/workspace?showDetailedCharges=true&month={{month}}&year={{year}}"
        class="plain-link txt-primary txt-bold"
        style="color: #f89b41; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;"
      >${{cents-to-dollars totalBill}}</a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      Kindly add your card details in the
      <a
        href="https://app.patr.cloud/workspace"
        class="plain-link txt-primary"
        style="color: #f89b41; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;"
      >billing</a>
      section of Patr at the earliest.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      Lack of payment will result in the
      deletion of your resources on
      <strong
        class="txt-light"
        style="color:#ffffff"
      >{{deadline}}</strong>.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td
      class="para txt-light"
      style="padding-top: 1rem; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.3px; line-height: 1.3;"
    >
      If you are facing any issues, please
      reach out to us at
      <a
        href="mailto:suppport@patr.cloud"
        class="plain-link txt-primary"
        title="Contact Patr support"
        style="color: #f89b41; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;"
      >suppport@patr.cloud</a>.
    </td>
  </tr>
{{> container-end}}